# Filosign API routes

Backend: **`apps/server`**. **`/api`** is **oRPC** on **`/api/rpc`** and **OpenAPI UI** on **`/api/api-reference`** — see [`api/orpc/hono-mount.ts`](apps/server/api/orpc/hono-mount.ts). Procedure handlers live under [`api/handlers/*`](apps/server/api/handlers/) and compose [`api/orpc/router.ts`](apps/server/api/orpc/router.ts). [`api/routes/router.ts`](apps/server/api/routes/router.ts) mounts only **JWT optional auth** + hybrid middleware (no REST JSON carve-outs). Details in **[`AGENTS.md`](AGENTS.md)**.

## Conventions

- **Responses:** Native procedure outputs; **`ORPCError`** in handlers (`api/handlers/`).
- **Auth:** `optionalJwtWalletForOrpc` sets **`ctx.var.userWallet`** when Bearer JWT verifies (**invalid Bearer is skipped** → anonymous context). **`authenticatedProcedure`** (`api/orpc/procedures.ts`) throws **`UNAUTHORIZED`** via oRPC when the wallet is absent.
- **Debug logs:** JWT verify failures logs only when **`DEBUG=true`** ([`env.ts`](apps/server/env.ts)).
- **Inputs:** Zod at the procedure boundary (`.input` / `.safeParse`).
- **Fallible async:** **`tryCatch`** / **`tryCatchSync`** ([`patterns.mdc`](patterns.mdc)); map failures to **`ORPCError`** in handlers.

## TanStack Query (React SDK)

- **`rpcQuery`** exposes **`createTanstackQueryUtils` per subtree** — `filosign` root + **`auth`**, **`files`**, **`sharing`**, **`storage`**, **`users`**, **`tx`**, plus leaf utils for **`healthCheck`** / **`runtime`** ([`rpc-query-utils.ts`](packages/react-sdk/src/orpc/rpc-query-utils.ts)).

## Client

Consume **`useFilosignContext().rpc`** (and **`session`**); prefer **`rpcQuery`** for query/mutation helpers. Direct **`fetch` PUT** only to URLs from **`storage.presignPut`** / file upload presign flows. **`apps/client`** stays thin (**`AGENTS.md`**).
